#*
Used to generate image thumbnail img tag src attribute only.
  - fieldId - the field into which the data is inserted.
  - itemId  - the image ID
  - width the image width
  - height the image height
  - rotation 0-3
  - milliseconds - modification date of the image
*#
/thumbnail/data?sourceType=IMAGE&sourceId=$itemId&sourceParentId=$fieldId&width=$width&height=$height&rotation=$rotation&time=$milliseconds